minor corrections in &quot;track the changes&quot; mode. \r\nIt would be beneficial for the authors to re-read the final version after accepting my editings.\r\n','Servet Dogdu','I think this paper is an important contribution to new species in the Mediterranean coast of Turkey.\r\nI corrected the sentences that needed minor corrections in &quot;track the changes&quot; mode. \r\nIt would be beneficial for the authors to re-read the final version after accepting my editings.\r\n','NULL','../reviewreports/tes-0895455-56_2.docx','13-07-2024',5,4,5,0,1),(57,91,9,'2024-07-13',NULL,-1,'',-1,0,NULL,'Yakup Kutlu',NULL,NULL,'','',0,0,0,0,0),(58,88,2928,'2024-07-13',NULL,-1,'',-1,0,NULL,'Yakup Kutlu',NULL,NULL,'','',0,0,0,1,0),(59,85,1,'2024-07-20',NULL,-1,'',-1,0,NULL,'Yakup Kutlu',NULL,NULL,'','',0,0,0,1,0),(60,101,2961,'2024-07-27','2024-07-30',2,'',1,0,'The article reported  similarity and classification Analysis of AI tools such as chatgGPT, Gemini and Copilot. The study is suitable for publication in Tethys journal  but some necessary correction should be done :\r\nThere are some Turkish texts in text start in page 4. There are some grammatical errors. The caption order and formats are not correct and should be corrected.','Yakup Kutlu','.','NULL','NULL','30-07-2024',4,4,4,0,1),(61,101,2962,'2024-07-27',NULL,-1,'',-1,0,NULL,'Yakup Kutlu',NULL,NULL,'','',0,0,0,0,0),(62,108,9,'2024-07-28','2024-07-28',1,'',1,0,'it can be accepted as it is','Yakup Kutlu','no','NULL','NULL','28-07-2024',5,5,5,1,1),(63,108,2923,'2024-07-28',NULL,-1,'',-1,0,NULL,'Yakup Kutlu',NULL,NULL,'','',0,0,0,1,1),(64,108,2918,'2024-07-28','2024-07-29',2,'',1,0,'-','Yakup Kutlu','-','../reviewreports/TES-1084649-64.docx','../reviewreports/TES-1084649-64_2.docx','29-07-2024',4,5,5,1,1),(65,101,2963,'2024-07-28','2024-07-30',2,'',1,0,'\r\nThe article titled &quot;Similarity and Classification Analysis in Turkish Question Generation of AI tools According to Bloom’s Taxonomy&quot; is a comparative study on the use of chatgpt gemini and copilot, which are current AI tools.\r\n\r\n- the study title is appropriate\r\n- the references are appropriate and sufficient\r\n\r\nit can be accepted after the following corrections are made.\r\n\r\n- the Turkish texts are available in text and what does mean &quot;Yeniden Yapılandırılmış Bloom Taksonomisinin Bilişsel Süreç X. Basamağı: &quot; in page 4\r\n- there are some grammatical errors\r\n- they should be aligned formally\r\n- the titles are not correct and should be corrected','Yakup Kutlu','\r\nThe article titled &quot;Similarity and Classification Analysis in Turkish Question Generation of AI tools According to Bloom’s Taxonomy&quot; is a comparative study on the use of chatgpt gemini and copilot, which are current AI tools.\r\n\r\n- the study title is appropriate\r\n- the references are appropriate and sufficient\r\n\r\nit can be accepted after the following corrections are made.\r\n\r\n- the Turkish texts are available in text and what does mean &quot;Yeniden Yapılandırılmış Bloom Taksonomisinin Bilişsel Süreç X. Basamağı: &quot; in page 4\r\n- there are some grammatical errors\r\n- they should be aligned formally\r\n- the titles are not correct and should be corrected','NULL','NULL','30-07-2024',4,4,4,0,1),(66,109,2923,'2024-07-30',NULL,-1,'',-1,0,NULL,'Yakup Kutlu',NULL,NULL,'','',0,0,0,0,0),(67,109,2928,'2024-07-30',NULL,-1,'',-1,0,NULL,'Yakup Kutlu',NULL,NULL,'','',0,0,0,0,0),(68,109,2924,'2024-07-30','2024-07-30',2,'',1,0,'Dear Authors\r\nIt is recommended that corrections to the paper be made according to the referee&#39;s advice.','Yakup Kutlu','Dear Editor,\r\n\r\nThe paper must be corrected as indicated in the text. The paper can be accepted after the corrections.\r\n\r\nBest regards','NULL','../reviewreports/TES-1090917-68_2.docx','30-07-2024',3,3,4,0,1),(69,109,9,'2024-07-30','2024-07-30',2,'',1,0,'1-Comet assay picture from the speciements should be added\r\n2-Graphical abstract  does not represent the M&S, so 