entral Mediterranean Sea). Mediterranean Marine Science, 10(1), 55-72.\", \"Ricker, W. E. (1973). Linear regressions in fishery research. Journal of the Fisheries Board of Canada, 30(3), 409-434.\", \"Rinelli, P., Bottari, T., Florio, G., Romeo, T., Giordano, D., Greco, S. (2005). Observations on distribution and biology of Galeus melastomus (Chondrichthyes, Scyliorhinidae) in the southern Tyrrhenian Sea (central Mediterranean). Cybium, 29(1), 41-46.\", \"Triay Portella, R., Gonz\\u00e1lez P\\u00e9rez, J. A., Lorenzo Nespereira, J. M., Gonz\\u00e1lez Pajuelo, J. M. (2023). Length-weight relationship of 15 species of deep-water chondrichthyans in the Canary Islands (eastern-central Atlantic). Cybium. 37(2), 350-353.\", \"Tursi, A. R., D\'Onghia, G. (1993). Observations on population biology of catshark Galeus melastomus (Chondrichthyes, Scyliorhinidae) in the Ionian Sea. Cybium, 17(3), 187-196.\"], \"language\": \"eng\", \"license\": \"cc-by-4.0\", \"journal_title\": \"Tethys Environmental Science\", \"journal_volume\": \"1\", \"journal_issue\": \"3\", \"journal_pages\": \"135-1433\", \"imprint_publisher\": \"Tethys Environmental Science\", \"notes\": \"ISSN : 3023-7343\", \"upload_type\": \"publication\", \"publication_type\": \"article\", \"prereserve_doi\": {\"doi\": \"10.5281/zenodo.13733205\", \"recid\": 13733205}}, \"title\": \"Length-Weight Relationship of the Blackmouth Catshark (Galeus melastomus Rafinesque, 1810) on the Turkish Coasts of the Mediterranean Sea\", \"links\": {\"self\": \"https://zenodo.org/api/deposit/depositions/13733205\", \"html\": \"https://zenodo.org/deposit/13733205\", \"badge\": \"https://zenodo.org/badge/doi/.svg\", \"files\": \"https://zenodo.org/api/deposit/depositions/13733205/files\", \"bucket\": \"https://zenodo.org/api/files/92deaf61-e220-40fc-ba38-7be5cef50413\", \"latest_draft\": \"https://zenodo.org/api/deposit/depositions/13733205\", \"latest_draft_html\": \"https://zenodo.org/deposit/13733205\", \"publish\": \"https://zenod