Fleming, 1822 (Gastropoda: Euthyneura: Pulmonata: Onchidiidae). ZooKeys, 972, 1-224.\r<br>Goulding, T. C., Munawar, K., Shau, H. T., Rebecca, A., Cumming, B. D. (2022). Global diversification and evolutionary history of onchidiid slugs (Gastropoda: Pulmonata). Molecular Phylogenetics and Evolution, 168, 107360.\r<br>Maniei, F., Espeland, M., Movahedi, M., Wägele, H.  (2020). Description of a new Peronia species (Gastropoda: Eupulmonata: Onchidiidae) from Iran, Persian Gulf. Zootaxa, 4758(3), 501-531.\r<br>MolluscaBase (Eds). (2024). MolluscaBase. www.molluscabase.org, versión (10/2024).\r<br>Zhang, K., Wang, D., Shen, H., Qian, J., Guan, J., Wu, H., Gao, Y. (2016). Redescription of Platevindex mortoni (Gastropoda: Eupulmonata: Onchidiidae) from China. Molluscan Research, 37 (1), 72-78.',1,4,'171-178',171,2024,1,470,474,0,'10.5281/zenodo.14017324','14017324','{\"created\": \"2024-10-31T11:28:03.921414+00:00\", \"modified\": \"2024-10-31T11:28:03.991541+00:00\", \"id\": 14017324, \"conceptrecid\": \"14017323\", \"metadata\": {\"title\": \"Taxonomic study of Peronia peronii (Cuvier, 1804) (Mollusca: Gastropoda: Onchidiidae) from the Karachi coast (northern Arabian Sea)\", \"publication_date\": \"2024-12-15\", \"description\": \"Onchidiidae species are generally found in sandy, muddy, or rocky habitats within the middle and upper intertidal zones, respectively. The diversity of their species remains poorly understood, and their taxonomy has not been revised. Genus Peronia has nine presently accepted species. The current analysis is the first report on taxonomy of Peronia peronii on the Karachi coast. The results are compared with the data published by other authors.\", \"access_right\": \"open\", \"creators\": [{\"name\": \"Arshia Naz Khatib\", \"affiliation\": null}, {\"name\": \"Farhana S. Ghory*\", \"affiliation\": null}], \"keywords\": [\"Taxonomy\", \"Peronia peronii\", \"Gastropoda\", \"Onchidiidae\", \"Karachi coast\", \"northern Arabian Sea.\"], \"references\": 