7}}, \"title\": \"Feeding-Related Behavioral Changes of Green Sea Turtle Chelonia mydas in Mersin Bay, Northeastern Mediterranean\", \"links\": {\"self\": \"https://zenodo.org/api/deposit/depositions/17220217\", \"html\": \"https://zenodo.org/deposit/17220217\", \"badge\": \"https://zenodo.org/badge/doi/.svg\", \"files\": \"https://zenodo.org/api/deposit/depositions/17220217/files\", \"bucket\": \"https://zenodo.org/api/files/b2206967-6a07-4d22-bc46-e5190572cafb\", \"latest_draft\": \"https://zenodo.org/api/deposit/depositions/17220217\", \"latest_draft_html\": \"https://zenodo.org/deposit/17220217\", \"publish\": \"https://zenodo.org/api/deposit/depositions/17220217/actions/publish\", \"edit\": \"https://zenodo.org/api/deposit/depositions/17220217/actions/edit\", \"discard\": \"https://zenodo.org/api/deposit/depositions/17220217/actions/discard\", \"newversion\": \"https://zenodo.org/api/deposit/depositions/17220217/actions/newversion\"}, \"record_id\": 17220217, \"owner\": 1087900, \"files\": [], \"state\": \"unsubmitted\", \"submitted\": false}'),(145,'Okan Akyol','okan.akyol@ege.edu.tr','','',0,0,'okan.akyol@ege.edu.tr','Additional Record of Cheilodipterus novemstriatus (Rüppell, 1838) from the Aegean Sea (Gökova Bay, Türkiye)','',0,'On 23 July 2025, the schools of Cheilodiperus novemstriatus associated with three black longspine urchins (Diadema setosum) over a hard substrate in the shoreline of Akbük, Gökova Bay were observed during snorkeling. The depth of the substrate was recorded as 1 m. This ichthyological note presents the second record of C. novemstriatus from the southeastern Aegean Sea. Since 2010, the species has been documented in eight different locations, and ongoing westward and northward spread.','Cheilodipterus novemstriatus, additional record, snorkelling, southeastern Aegean Sea, Gökova Bay','Natural Science','../uploadfiles/Tethys_EnvSci _TES-1451856-R1.pdf','../uploadfiles/Tethys_EnvSci _TES-1451856-R1.docx','../paperimages/Tethys_EnvSci _T